      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a dedicated new owner to bring it back to its former glory. While it currently requires significant mechanical attention and bodywork, it serves as an excellent foundation for a restoration project or a valuable source of parts. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge at a great price, this is the one for you!",
