    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, currently maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits zero signs of wear, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been verified to meet the most stringent performance standards, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from a new delivery. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
