      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory-original luster with zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professionally applied ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and the original carpets have been protected by factory mats since new. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The engine bay is detailed and free of any weeping or oxidation, reflecting a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that shows no signs of age. Includes all original keys, window sticker, and a complete maintenance binder.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
